<br />

<br />
   So the crux of your argument is that Bards are better at crowd control <span style="font-weight: bold">exclusively</span> because their durability outweighs the enormous disadvantages they possess in every other aspect.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
